mentation efﬁciency. Moreover, we computed the Dice coefﬁcient between automatically segmented and manually a','https://journals.lww.com/international-journal-of-surgery/fulltext/2024/10000/ct_based_ai_model_for_predicting_therapeutic.53.aspx');
